      <T n="text">0x40B5C713<!--When you open the Small Business, potential customers will start arriving! Having fair prices and maintaining good relationships with customers will invite them to explore all that your Small Business has to offer.\n\nDepending on the type of Small Business you have set up, it's important to ensure that <b><font color='#199C2C'>Retail Displays</font></b> are stocked with goods, customers have everything they need to engage in the Business Activities you have set, and that the premises look appealing. Why not have your Sim socialize with their customers while you're at it?--></T>
    </U>
